{
  "text": "Out of the Seth material, we have a statement here. Seth says that each entity here on Earth is one aspect or part of a higher self or older soul, which has many aspects or parts in many dimensions, all of which learn lessons which enable the higher self to progress in a balanced manner. Am I to understand from this, is it correct, that there are, shall we say, possibly many experiences similar to the one that we experience here in third density that are governed by a single higher self. Is this correct? I am Ra. The correctness of this statement is variable, the more in balance an entity becomes the less the possibility, probability vortices may need to be explored in parallel experiences.",
